**New Graduation Information--May 15, 2020**

Listed below is additional information that students need to know regarding graduation on June 6, 2020 at Ford Pavilion starting at 7:00 P.M. The district will release information periodically leading up to graduation, so please be on the lookout for our continued communication.

*Each senior can invite 10 guests to graduation;

*Seniors will receive tickets in two (2) units of five (5);

*One unit of 5 tickets will have seats located under the pavilion; the other unit of 5 tickets will have seats located on the lawn;

*Only household units may sit together.

As always, we thank you for your continued support and patience as the district works through the COVID-19 guidelines and serves our students in the best way possible.

