Below is information regarding make-up time (days) for the weather days missed on January 16 and 17, 2018. The district has received information that a waiver for those days will be considered, so the district administration will go through the three step process for approval.

1. The district site-base committee will be presented an opportunity to approve the waiver;

2. The school board will have the same opportunity to approve the waiver;

3. If approved by both the district site-base committee and school board the waiver will be submitted to the Texas Education Agency for approval.

Given the process for waiver approval, February 19, 2018, President's Day, will remain a district holiday. If the waiver is denied, the district will revise the calendar and the make-up time (days) will occur between March 5 and June 8, 2018. The district should have final approval information regarding the waiver by March 2, 2018.

